There are two distinct questions here and they have different answers.

Question 1 — What categories/sources is this table theoretically capable of collecting?

This answer lives in Microsoft's documentation, not in the data. The table in your workspace only shows you what has been configured and sent. For the full list of every possible category:

https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-monitor/reference/tables/azurediagnostics

That page lists every Azure service that can write to this table and what Category value it uses. This is your authoritative reference for what is possible versus what is active.

