Source	Primarily Captures	Security Value
Azure Firewall DNS Proxy (AzureDiagnostics)	All outbound DNS queries from VNet resources — public and internal	HIGH — catches malware beaconing, suspicious domains, data exfiltration via DNS
Private DNS Resolver (DNSQueryLogs)	Internal name resolution — private endpoints, hybrid on-prem lookups, policy-controlled queries	MEDIUM — catches lateral movement to internal resources, policy violations, unusual internal lookups
